Package data

Class LIFOFixedSize<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • data.LIFOFixedSize<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - 
    public class LIFOFixedSize<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Keep a buffer of some objects. Oldest gets thrown out to keep the size at/below a maximum. Using an iterator, you can go through it LIFO-style. Based around an ArrayDeque, but with push being the only way to add elements.
    Author:
    matt
